			<td class="table-card-td-body" style="line-height: 24px; text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 20px 24px;">
			<p align="center"><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a class="logo-anchor" href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fwww.taskade.com/1/01000193781570f9-4e2409d4-d0fc-46dd-91fa-4fd47f03985e-000000/XRxT2b21jX8FlNWLkRylyJd1-vU=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: underline; color: #ff2d60; display: block;"><img class="left" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1666116818.png" style="border: 0px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; width: 42px; height: 42px;" /></a></span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;">Hi there&nbsp; 🐑</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;">Ready to organize like a pro?&nbsp;Taskade&#39;s unique structure helps you bring order to chaos. Discover how to get the most out of our &nbsp;<a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F7400371873427--Hierarchy-Structure-in-Taskade/1/01000193781570f9-4e2409d4-d0fc-46dd-91fa-4fd47f03985e-000000/LarM8Pmm-itl8sk49T3HWdZekXA=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">hierarchy and structure</a> today!</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;">Before you dive into the details, <a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv=ITXyJivODnc/1/01000193781570f9-4e2409d4-d0fc-46dd-91fa-4fd47f03985e-000000/mKfFp0L8MxSs28OA_yoJw1H8Iq8=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">check out our video tutorial</a> to see it in action!</span></p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">🗃 Workspaces</h1>

			<p>Your top-level productivity space where you can store all your projects&nbsp;and folders.&nbsp; Invite team members here to unlock the full power of Taskade, including unlimited AI capabilites and more.&nbsp;<span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F360015915474--Manage-a-Workspace/1/01000193781570f9-4e2409d4-d0fc-46dd-91fa-4fd47f03985e-000000/ShbI2T024OdneygHl7zrgQNWDqI=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a>. </span></p>

			<h2 class="table-card-td-body-p-title"><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698681157.png" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></h2>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">&nbsp;</h1>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">&nbsp;🚋 Folders</h1>

			<p>Your go-to for organizing different teams, clients, and projects within a workspace. Folders are private by default, keeping your work secure until you decide to share. You can also choose to share Folders externally.&nbsp;<span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F11933152036115--Folder-Permissions/1/01000193781570f9-4e2409d4-d0fc-46dd-91fa-4fd47f03985e-000000/IRqlHcR9aM-1qPHCop2czl0dTzM=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a>. </span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698681167.png" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></p>

			<p>&nbsp;</p>

			<p>&nbsp;</p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">📝 Projects</h1>

			<p>The heart of your collaboration! Turn your tasks and notes into actionable steps, and collaborate in real-time. Switch views for the optimal project visualization from list view to mind map,&nbsp;kanban board, and more.&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F360016023373/1/01000193781570f9-4e2409d4-d0fc-46dd-91fa-4fd47f03985e-000000/QY_DaSSS458G1xb3D6uyzbiZm7E=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a>.</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698682069.gif" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></p>

			<p>&nbsp;</p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">🧱 Blocks and ✅ Tasks/Sub-Tasks</h1>

			<p>Visualize your projects as tree-structured outlines with cascading tasks.&nbsp;Our flexible structure makes task management a breeze.&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F360015872614--Outlining-101/1/01000193781570f9-4e2409d4-d0fc-46dd-91fa-4fd47f03985e-000000/xgIHLinvsNf38yQE1ll3FG57jxE=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a>.</span></p>

			<p>Every task can be turned into a bullet point and more. These are The building blocks of your projects. Create, assign, and manage tasks easily.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F4409874717715--Project-Add-Ons/1/01000193781570f9-4e2409d4-d0fc-46dd-91fa-4fd47f03985e-000000/NMtgiY_csYYRCdNHGosxQZ2K8w8=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Learn more</a>.</span></p>

			<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;"><img alt="Taskade AI" src="https://www.taskade.com/newsletters/uploads/1698681937.gif" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 20px; outline: none; text-decoration: none; max-width: 695px; width: 100%;" /></span></p>

			<h1 class="table-card-td-body-p-title">&nbsp;</h1>

			<p class="table-card-td-body-p-description" style="font-family: Inter, "><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;">Thank you for being part of our journey. Stay tuned for more exciting updates!</span></p>

			<p class="table-card-td-body-p-description" style="font-family: Inter, "><span style="font-family:Helvetica Neue;">Do you have any questions? Visit our <a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fhelp.taskade.com/1/01000193781570f9-4e2409d4-d0fc-46dd-91fa-4fd47f03985e-000000/QQm938sRmi6W6WXdHPQGTQfO4_c=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">Help Center</a> or <a href="https://3fxyvvmr.r.us-east-1.awstrack.me/L0/https:%2F%2Fwww.taskade.com%2Fcontact/1/01000193781570f9-4e2409d4-d0fc-46dd-91fa-4fd47f03985e-000000/OsWRcoFEROm0Ep0aVAhn5LJmvc8=402" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-decoration: none; color: #ff2d60;">let us know</a>. 😊</span></p>

